long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Game Description
Stick Monkey is stuck! He has a handy stretchy stick to move throughout his adventures, but needs your help to decide how far to stretch!

Note:- You can Play More Categories Game In This Extension.

You must stretch just enough for Monkey to safely move to safe ground. If it’s too short or too long, Monkey tumbles down below! Ouch!

Game Instructions
Tap the arrow to start.

Tap and hold on the screen to guess how long you need to stretch the stick for Monkey to move to safe ground. Be wise, as if it’s too short or too long, your game is over. Good luck!
